Interface PriorityQueue<K,D>

Type Parameters:
K - type of the key value
D - type of the data object
All Known Implementing Classes:
DHeap
public interface PriorityQueue<K,D>
Interface for a generic Priority Queue data structure composed of nodes of type PriorityQueueNode containing pairs of data objects associated with a key
